#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/transformation_masks.rst:1
msgid "How to use transformation masks in Krita."
msgstr "如何在 Krita 中使用變形遮罩。"

#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/transformation_masks.rst:17
msgid "Transform Masks"
msgstr "變形遮罩"

#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/transformation_masks.rst:19
msgid ""
"Rather than working with a brush to affect the mask, transform masks allow "
"you to transform (move, rotate, shear, scale and perspective) a layer "
"without applying the transform directly to the paint layer and making it "
"permanent."
msgstr "和使用畫筆來影響遮罩不同，變形遮罩是可以使用（移動、旋轉、剪切、縮放和透視）的圖層，而且不用套用或合併圖層上的效果或是濾鏡遮罩。"

#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/transformation_masks.rst:21
msgid ""
"In the same way that Filter and Transparency Masks can be attached to a "
"Paint layer and are non-destructive, so too can the Transform Mask."
msgstr "就像濾鏡遮罩和透明度遮罩一樣，變形遮罩也可以附加到顏料圖層，一樣是非破壞性可隨時修改的。"

#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/transformation_masks.rst:25
msgid ""
"Transform masks can also be used in conjunction with the :ref:"
"`animation_curves_docker` to :dfn:`Tween` an animation."
msgstr "變形遮罩也可以與 :ref:`animation_curves_docker` 結合使用於 :dfn:`Tween` 動畫。"

#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/transformation_masks.rst:28
msgid "Adding a Transform Mask"
msgstr "增加變形遮罩"

#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/transformation_masks.rst:30
msgid "First add a transform mask to an existing layer."
msgstr "首先對現有的顏料圖層 ( 或是群組圖層 ) 增加變形遮罩。"

#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/transformation_masks.rst:31
msgid "Select the :ref:`transform_tool`."
msgstr "請選擇 :ref:`transform_tool` 工具。"

#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/transformation_masks.rst:32
msgid ""
"Select any of the transform modes in the Tools Options dock and, with the "
"transform mask selected, apply them on the layer."
msgstr "在“工具選項”工作介面中選擇任一種變型模式，並且在選取變形遮罩的情況下將它應用到圖層上。"

#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/transformation_masks.rst:33
msgid "Hit apply."
msgstr "點擊工具選項界面下方「套用」按鈕。"

#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/transformation_masks.rst:34
msgid ""
"Toggle the transform visibility to see the difference between the original "
"and the transform applied."
msgstr "切換變形遮罩的眼睛圖示 ( 可見性 ) 可以查看原本圖像和有套用變形之間的差異。"

#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/transformation_masks.rst:38
msgid ""
"Affine transforms, like Move, Rotate, Shear, Scale and Perspective get "
"updated instantly once the original is updated. Other transforms like Warp, "
"Cage and Liquify take up much more processing power, and to not to waste "
"that, Krita only updates those every three seconds."
msgstr ""
"再製 ( 仿射 ) 變換，如移動、旋轉、剪切、縮放和透視，在原始來源( 可能是群組圖層的再製 )更新後立即更新。 其他變換如 網面、外框 和 液化 "
"會佔用更多的處理效能，為了避免浪費效能，Krita 每三秒更新計算一次。"

#: ../../reference_manual/layers_and_masks/transformation_masks.rst:40
msgid ""
"To edit a transform, select the transform mask, and try to use the transform "
"tool on the layer. The transform mode will be the same as the stored "
"transform, regardless of what transform you had selected. If you switch "
"transform modes, the transformation will be undone."
msgstr ""
"要編輯變形，請選擇變形遮罩，然後在畫面中使用變形工具。 不管當初您選擇什麼變形模式，變形模式都會和當初使用的一致。 "
"如果這時候切換變形模式，變形將被取消還原。"

